trans-unit.source: Obtains the file locations of XML Schema documents for use in populating a Web services discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar filplatser för XML-schemadokument för användning i fylla Web services discovery-dokumentet.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The XmlSchemaSearchPattern class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern> class and is employed by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> class's <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method, which handles an HTTP request for a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: XmlSchemaSearchPattern klassen ärver från abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>klassen och anställda av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler>klassens <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metod som hanterar HTTP-begäran för en discovery-dokumentet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>

trans-unit.source: Normally, none of these classes need to be used directly by a developer.
trans-unit.target: Ingen av dessa klasser behöver normalt användas direkt av en utvecklare.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.XmlSchemaSearchPattern"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.XmlSchemaSearchPattern"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference"></xref> object for a given discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference"> </xref> objekt för en given discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The concrete <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference> class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> class.
trans-unit.target: Den konkreta <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference>klassen ärver från en abstrakt <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference>klass.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference> instance contains the location of the .xsd file.
The file system path of the XML Schema document.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference"></xref> object that specifies the file name for an XML Schema document.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference"> </xref> objekt som anger filnamnet för en XML-schemadokument.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file name pattern to use as a search target.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar filnamnsmönster som ska användas som ett mål för sökning.

trans-unit.source: The pattern "*.xsd" indicates an XML Schema document extension.
